{"tid":1744923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【集思廣益】大家一齊諗下我哋可以點贏","createTime":"2019-11-22T03:35:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T09:26:31.000Z","uid":221035,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3d5dac7834bf9d23d6faf1ba775af589cb677b91","tid":1744923,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:35:35.000Z","msg":"贏嘅意思，我理解唔單單係五大訴求，而係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港擺脫支共嘅控制，並且享有民主政制，真正建立屬於我哋嘅香港</span></strong>（利申：全部係講長遠，唔係一兩年嘅事）<br />\n<br />\n首先簡單解構香港嘅權力核心，就係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>中共+商界+建制政黨嘅龐大管治集團，並以軍警作為鎮壓機器</strong></span>，我哋要對準呢四樣嘢去攻擊，而實贏嘅方法有好多，我盡量list out<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">針對中共</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">國際戰線</span></strong>：歐美多國同時對中共實施強硬制裁，中共收皮；宣布中英聯合聲明無效，香港暫時歸英；聯合國派維和部隊進駐香港，成為中立之地；連結真。外國勢力去支援革命，例如大量資金和武裝<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">中共戰線</span></strong>：黨內溫和派鬥贏習近平，結束獨裁；革命輸出去中國，中共因內戰而亡；支爆<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">針對商界</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">經濟戰線</span></strong>：股票系統失靈或證券業大罷工，香港停市；建立真。黃色經濟圈，切斷中共水喉；中共玩死商家，大家反面<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">工運戰線</span></strong>：而工會聯盟推動改革，推冧而中共為首嘅商家；而持續多年的工運和罷工，令香港的權力集團出現內部改變<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">針對建制</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>體制內路線</strong></span>：用極懸殊民意直接壟斷議會，奪取立法權；持續派人進入政府及建制政黨，他日掌權之後反轉豬肚<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">針對軍警</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>勇武抗爭</strong></span>：取得武裝成立革命軍，開啟全面內戰，香港北愛化；殺死高官或軍警首領，直接奪權；軍警因不同原因倒戈"},{"pid":"7b2062729be4340c4aa97025f74f1c3ccded8e39","tid":1744923,"uid":221035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:35:47.000Z","msg":"大家一齊集思廣益下"},{"pid":"58cd456cbe4872cf941bfa40a06d7e5e9182285e","tid":1744923,"uid":221035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:36:12.000Z","msg":"尤其覺得冇乜目標，有啲迷失嘅時候，就一齊諗清楚我哋嘅目標係咩"},{"pid":"3b1e390e68c255402295b901bf4738a2ee53bedd","tid":1744923,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:36:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b852c8602d15d78bc729c7466f1cbbe9fcf472a","tid":1744923,"uid":44742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:37:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e4f26188a075c4f4fb822706747f376220cea65","tid":1744923,"uid":86509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:37:44.000Z","msg":"離間中美兩方<br />\n挑起兩方人民互相排斥情緒<br />\n引發ww3"},{"pid":"7f4eec04dca730c6ec12779b7c396c2ecc52a145","tid":1744923,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:37:55.000Z","msg":"只要其中一個方法成功，都已經可以贏"},{"pid":"c831076baf980d1399587dad6f94e26f64b43e8f","tid":1744923,"uid":281516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:38:15.000Z","msg":"選舉近了, 共黨B隊出動!!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1744825\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1744825</a>"},{"pid":"f7a7e35f9a40d8365b8ba07d40c4c02e72b40c34","tid":1744923,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e4f26188a075c4f4fb822706747f376220cea65","tid":1744923,"uid":86509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:37:44.000Z","msg":"離間中美兩方<br />\n挑起兩方人民互相排斥情緒<br />\n引發ww3"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:38:22.000Z","msg":"呢個係「歐美多國同時對中共實施強硬制裁，中共收皮」嘅進階版"},{"pid":"32b2c63407e4138a9cedba2ca9742725e54d33cc","tid":1744923,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:39:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5bd331cef4cfd41b4c9a3cda8743ed735eb742b","tid":1744923,"uid":245849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:39:28.000Z","msg":"我個人只對軍武建設比較有意見同建議，先留名，晚上覆。"},{"pid":