則會被失踪。<br />\n<br />\n麻煩繼續幫推：<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">咋咋林啦！</span>連登以外幫手文宣鍵戰，以下正皮、加推、幫手做，時間無多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出街全部對家街站，死得啦，麻煩認真幫推呢個整合左既行動PO啦，再唔做的野輸死喇：</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>【行動post】《緊急》全民選舉文宣+鍵盤戰</strong></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1743618\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1743618</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><ins>原PO<br />\n選舉文宣！文宣！文宣呀！唔夠對家多呀！的牆無曬喇！</ins></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ezmgyS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ezmgyS</a>"},{"pid":"ab4948830b4665069dfad3da58d2f516187acd24","tid":1744923,"uid":323228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5167cc692db99b4ee04dad0e9a5c276c90fdcf05","tid":1744923,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:39:33.000Z","msg":"打長期戰一定要玩滲透"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:52:15.000Z","msg":"同埋網軍！<br />\n點解重要？唔重要支共同蘇聯唔使比咁多錢請三毛五毛打世界戰啦。"},{"pid":"0ee32a79c548a14eb43b76e4535cdef2249a2554","tid":1744923,"uid":10258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:53:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c5838ac23d6fc8f20a8ce818a492ec1b8468513","tid":1744923,"uid":143210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:58:02.000Z","msg":"網上戰線要繼續以甴近平同六四留名來驅魔"},{"pid":"cfb6462e4290cf03436065cc94c5e73005d6d7e9","tid":1744923,"uid":245849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"156e3e48a9f99f3ebb000ac60b15c39f27b46817","tid":1744923,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5bd331cef4cfd41b4c9a3cda8743ed735eb742b","tid":1744923,"uid":245849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:39:28.000Z","msg":"我個人只對軍武建設比較有意見同建議，先留名，晚上覆。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:40:33.000Z","msg":"但我覺得軍武係最難，因為國際社會唔會俾香港真係內戰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:21:13.000Z","msg":"逆向思考：中共真係會單純因為歐美外交勢力而放棄香港主權嘅可能性一樣係低，所以要多邊發展"},{"pid":"53dbf0c8562f5645e7ce86bf4e9b8dfdcd6bd1f3","tid":1744923,"uid":331142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:27:30.000Z","msg":"滲透建制陣營真係好緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔只繼續發展偽建制黨<br />\n仲要入真建制陣營甚至共產黨去攞情報<br />\n最後分化、篤灰、割蓆，任務完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遲啲好多80後or above可能會移民<br />\n但係可唔可以唔好放棄香港<br />\n<br />\n一係滲透海外中共勢力<br />\n一係建立外交團隊<br />\n<br />\n講返轉頭，要搞情報任務<br />\n首先就要有地下組織同溝通渠道<br />\n冇得用連登同TG channel傾秘密任務<br />\n問題係一個去中央化嘅秘密組織可以點run<br />\n定係分散秘密小隊各有各做"}]}